Package sx.blah.discord.util.audio.providers

This contains implementations of IAudioProvider.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioInputStreamProvider
    This represents an IAudioProvider implementation which wraps an AudioInputStream.
    FileProvider
    This extension of AudioInputStreamProvider attempts to create an AudioInputStream from the provided file and then provide based on that.
    GlobalProvider
    GlobalProvider allows for an IAudioProvider to provide the same audio across multiple IAudioManager instances.
    ProviderQueue
    The ProviderQueue is an IAudioProvider implementation which allows for audio providers to be queued so that as soon as a provider cannot provided data (i.e.
    URLProvider
    This extension of AudioInputStreamProvider attempts to create an AudioInputStream from the provided url and then provide based on that.
